Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:58.84,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}巧妙地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:03.68,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}联系起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:10.64,zw-ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\blur12\bord6\be8}连同这份情谊 永不分离
